          amet felis consectetur elementum vel a est.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <div class='social'>
          <a href='https://instragram.com/aradugbo' target='_blank'>
            <i class='lab la-instagram'></i>
          </a>
          <a href='https://twitter.com/your_app_twitter' target='_blank'><i
              class='lab la-twitter'
            ></i></a>
          <a href='https://facebook.com/your_app_facebook' target='_blank'><i
              class='lab la-facebook-square'
            ></i></a>
          <!-- <a href="https://linkedin.com/your_app_linkedin" target="_blank"
